plt.plot(df["date"], df["min"], label="Min Temp", marker="o")
plt.plot(df["date"], df["avg"], label="Avg Temp", marker="o")
plt.legend()
plt.title("Temperature Trend")
plt.xlabel("Date")
plt.ylabel("Â°C")
plt.show()

ğŸ§  5ï¸âƒ£ General Steps for Any API

Fetch the response:

